-- appendGen (++) :: Gen [a] -> Gen [a] -> Gen [a]
on appendGen(xs, ys)
    script
        property vs : xs
        on |位|()
            set v to |位|() of vs
            if missing value is not v then
                v
            else
                set vs to ys
                |位|() of ys
            end if
        end |位|
    end script
end appendGen
